'''Liu''' is a [[Chinese family name]]. The [[transliteration]] ''Liu'' can represent several [[Chinese characters]], the family names [[wiktionary:&#21129;|&#21129;]]; (&#21016; in [[Simplified Chinese character|Simplified Chinese]]) (''Lau'' in [[Cantonese (linguistics)|Cantonese]]), [[wiktionary:&#26611;|&#26611;]], [[wiktionary:&#30041;|&#30041;]] and [[wiktionary:&#20845;|&#20845;]]. In Vietnamese, the name can either take the form "Liễu" (in northern regions) or "Lưu" (in central or southern regions).  

In Cantonese transliteration, ''Liu'' is yet another name, [[wiktionary:&#24278;|&#24278;]].

&#21129; is an extremely popular name, as it was used by the ruling family of the [[Han Dynasty]] - a high point in the history of China.